garage.model

Class InvoiceSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • garage.model.InvoiceSystem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class InvoiceSystem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The InvoiceSystem class stores and handles any new invoices from previously closed tickets. There can only be one instance of an InvoiceSystem object at any given point once instantiated. The object can be accessed once imported using the getInstance() method.
    Version:
    1.0 Dec. 18, 2017.
    Author:
    Parra
    See Also:
